{"tid":1356240,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我認識藍色貨van 司機，有啲野想講","createTime":"2019-07-23T12:43:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T02:20:12.000Z","uid":217575,"like":14,"dislike":102,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"671e34498611fc103d1df4714d46e99d3a9f5d5b","tid":1356240,"uid":217575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:43:40.000Z","msg":"我以下講既野，都係經佢講返<br />\n個日佢並唔係特登要同市民作對，佢本身都係對市民既做法冇意見<br />\n但個日既遊行，我地係冇固定路線，佢係避唔開我地既路線先會相遇，佢同後面外藉司機加巴士司機一齊搬開路障諗住開條路走，但係途中係上面既人已經向佢架車dum野，佢嬲得濟先落車，結果就變成咁<br />\n我識左佢都一段時間，佢份人好好，唔係啲咁野蠻既人，佢本身都話，唔係工作關係佢都唔會去個到，佢已經同其他司機一樣，盡量搵路避，但我地係去到邊封到邊，冇留過一條路比佢地走。<br />\n同埋佢本身隻腳都係有事，佢係真係手停口停既，同埋根本係唔會夠個日打佢既人打。以家部車保險公司都唔會幫佢賠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我講大話我落地獄，不得好死"},{"pid":"0122b6a708c67ea149109a7e05d36250671e6525","tid":1356240,"uid":61398,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:44:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e04821dc0f295ecd274ce27c67ba5ea9603204f2","tid":1356240,"uid":102078,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:45:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">哦</span>"},{"pid":"669d8789ba8c449f119aabc8fd6c5ca792f864bf","tid":1356240,"uid":66254,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:55:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/178965725523592/posts/2344305415656268?s=663716082&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F178965725523592%2Fposts%2F2344305415656268%3Fs%3D663716082%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4T632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=8386af75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/178965725523592/posts/2344305415656268?s=663716082&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"c51ae9e3df89e337e0a90a5fb94f342acb421eb1","tid":1356240,"uid":70973,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:02:1